- NO BLACK & WHITE TEXT
- CLICK ANIMATIONS
  - 3 STAGES
    - NO CLICK/HOVER
    - HOVER
    - CLICK
- SPINNING LOADING SYMBOL WHEN PAGE LOADING
- SCSS, NOT CSS
- ADD CLASSES AND IDS WHENEVER POSSIBLE
- SEMANTIC HTML
  - IF AN HTML TERM EXISTS, USE IT (IE NAV INSTEAD OF DIV)
- NOTE: IF AN IMAGE IS PURELY DECORATIVE, YOU CAN SAVE IT TO YOUR LOCAL FILE
  - IF IT'S ASSOCIATED W YOUR DB, USE AWS